Facebook post by Noorie Noor Ananta, 1 January 2019. Caption: 'Eye am peace, Love & Light. Welcom 2019.' Photo shows Maa wearing pink knit hat, smiling, with Shiva Tripund tattoo clearly visible on forehead. 'Eye am' wordplay continues from 2018 (I am + Eye = third eye). Opening 2019 with peace and light — the transformation year. Aspect of Yug Parivartan: Avatar Identity — the third eye permanently visible, declaring peace and light as the frequency of the new year.
